# 2p_motion — host runs RIGHT and JET so we can see whether the
# client's view of the host's mech tracks the snapshot stream.
#
# At 1280x720 with the FFA-spawn fix, host spawns at lane 16 and
# client at lane 80 — far enough apart that a moving host should
# visibly approach the client over the course of a 6s match.

window 1280 720
out build/shots/net/host_motion
network host 24011
name HostA

# Match starts at ~tick 130. Host walks RIGHT and jets up to
# clear the col-55 wall. Pairs with 2p_motion.client.shot which
# walks LEFT — they meet near the middle of the map.
at 150 press right
at 200 press jet
at 260 release jet
at 350 press jet
at 410 release jet

at 150 shot match_start_t150
at 250 shot walking_t250
at 360 shot midway_t360
at 460 shot meeting_t460
at 530 release right
at 560 shot together_t560
at 720 shot summary_t720
at 780 end

contact_sheet sheet cols 3 cell 320 180

contact_sheet sheet cols 3 cell 320 180
